				<img width="1920" height="768" src="https://news.umbc.edu/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/KeithBowman_2-1920x768.jpg" class="attachment-gazette-single-thumbnail size-gazette-single-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" loading="lazy">			</div>
